The film revolves around a mysterious girl named Eclair who appears before Fairy Tail,
the world's most notorious wizard's guild. She lost all of her memories, except for the
imperative that she must deliver two Phoenix Stones somewhere. The stones may spell the
collapse of the magical world, and Natsu, Lucy and the rest of the Fairy Tail guild are
caught up in the intrigue.
